OL,3,GDumfries, Galloway, Lothian & Borders
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy and patchy rain clearing
OL,6,Faway eastwards this morning. Then the
OL,7,Frest of the day will be mainly dry
OL,8,Fwith some sunny spells. A few light
OL,9,Fshowers breaking out this afternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FAny showers dying out this
OL,12,Fevening, otherwise a dry end to the
OL,13,Fday. Then the rest of the night will
OL,14,Fbe dry with clear periods.
OL,15,
OL,16,CMonday:FMostly dry with variable
OL,17,Famounts of cloud, the odd shower
OL,18,Facross the Southern Uplands. A few
OL,19,Fshowers breaking out in the evening
OL,20,Felsewhere.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
